<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>규슈 가족여행 플래너</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap"/>
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #f5f2ec; --card: #fff; --primary: #2d6a4f; --primary-light: #52b788;
  --accent: #d4a017; --text: #1a1a2e; --muted: #6b7280; --border: #e5e0d8;
  --shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); --radius: 14px;
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }
body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); min-height: 100vh; }

/* STICKY TOP */
.sticky-top { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 200; box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.18); }

/* HEADER */
header { background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 14px 16px 10px; }
header h1 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; }
header p { font-size: 0.72rem; opacity: 0.8; margin-top: 2px; }
.header-meta { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-top: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }
.header-badge { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18); border-radius: 20px; padding: 3px 10px; font-size: 0.7rem; }
.sync-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: #94a3b8; display: inline-block; margin-right: 4px; }
.sync-dot.on { background: #4ade80; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
@keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.4} }

/* FIREBASE BANNER */
.fb-banner { background: #1e293b; color: #f1f5f9; padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 0.75rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.fb-banner.ok { background: #14532d; }
.btn-fb { background: #52b788; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 6px; padding: 4px 12px; font-size: 0.72rem; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 600; }

/* DAY NAV */
.day-nav { display: flex; gap: 5px; padding: 7px 12px; overflow-x: auto; background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); scrollbar-width: none; }
.day-nav::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
.day-btn { flex-shrink: 0; border: 2px solid var(--border); background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 4px 12px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; white-space: nowrap; transition: all .2s; }
.day-btn.active { background: var(--primary); border-color: var(--primary); color: white; }

/* NEARBY STRIP */
.nearby-strip { display: flex; gap: 5px; padding: 6px 12px 7px; overflow-x: auto; background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); scrollbar-width: none; align-items: center; }
.nearby-strip::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
.nearby-label { font-size: 0.67rem; color: var(--muted); white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; }
.nearby-btn { flex-shrink: 0; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 4px 11px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text); white-space: nowrap; }

/* WEATHER BAR */
.weather-bar { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #0284c7 100%); color: white; padding: 6px 14px; display: flex; gap: 8px; overflow-x: auto; scrollbar-width: none; align-items: center; }
.weather-bar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
.weather-day { flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 2px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 10px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); min-width: 58px; cursor: pointer; transition: background .2s; }
.weather-day:hover, .weather-day.active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
.weather-day .wd-date { font-size: 0.62rem; opacity: 0.85; }
.weather-day .wd-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; }
.weather-day .wd-temp { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600; }
.weather-day .wd-rain { font-size: 0.6rem; opacity: 0.85; }
.weather-loading { font-size: 0.72rem; opacity: 0.8; padding: 4px 0; }

/* MAIN */
main { padding: 0 0 80px; }

/* DAY SECTION */
.day-section { margin: 12px 12px 0; }
.day-header {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: var(--radius) var(--radius) 0 0;
  color: white; cursor: pointer; user-select: none;
}
.day-header-left { flex: 1; }
.day-header-title { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; }
.day-header-sub { font-size: 0.7rem; opacity: 0.85; margin-top: 2px; }
.day-header-weather { font-size: 0.8rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 8px; padding: 2px 8px; }
.day-toggle { font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.7; transition: transform .2s; }
.day-toggle.open { transform: rotate(180deg); }
.day-body { background: white; border-radius: 0 0 var(--radius) var(--radius); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-top: none; overflow: hidden; }

/* MEAL SECTION */
.meal-section { border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; }
.meal-section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.meal-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 8px 12px; background: #f9fafb; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; }
.meal-icon { font-size: 0.95rem; }
.meal-label { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--muted); flex: 1; }
.meal-add-btn { background: none; border: 1.5px dashed var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 2px 10px; font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; }
.meal-cards { min-height: 8px; padding: 4px 8px; }
.meal-cards.drag-over { background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 8px; }
.drop-indicator { height: 3px; background: #10b981; border-radius: 3px; margin: 2px 0; position: relative; }
.drop-indicator::before { content:''; position:absolute; left:-4px; top:-4px; width:10px; height:10px; background:#10b981; border-radius:50%; }
.drop-indicator::after  { content:''; position:absolute; right:-4px; top:-4px; width:10px; height:10px; background:#10b981; border-radius:50%; }
.sched-card.insert-above { border-top: 3px solid #10b981 !important; }
.sched-card.insert-below { border-bottom: 3px solid #10b981 !important; }

/* CARD */
.sched-card {
  background: white; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px;
  margin: 5px 0; padding: 10px 12px;
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px;
  cursor: grab; transition: box-shadow .2s, opacity .2s;
  position: relative;
}
.sched-card:active { cursor: grabbing; }
.sched-card.dragging { opacity: 0.4; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.18); }
.sched-card.drag-placeholder { background: #f0fdf4; border: 2px dashed var(--primary-light); opacity: 0.6; }

.card-drag-handle { color: #d1d5db; font-size: 1rem; padding-top: 2px; flex-shrink: 0; touch-action: none; }
.card-cat-dot { width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 5px; }
.card-body { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
.card-title { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.3; }
.card-time { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; cursor: pointer; }
.card-time:hover { color: var(--primary); }
.card-desc { font-size: 0.71rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; line-height: 1.5; white-space: pre-line; }
.card-actions { display: flex; gap: 4px; margin-top: 7px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.card-btn { border: 1.5px solid var(--border); background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 3px 9px; font-size: 0.65rem; font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; color: var(--muted); white-space: nowrap; }
.card-btn.danger { border-color: #fca5a5; color: #dc2626; }
.card-btn.primary { border-color: var(--primary-light); color: var(--primary); }

/* CAT COLORS */
.cat-transport { background: #6366f1; }
.cat-restaurant { background: #f59e0b; }
.cat-attraction { background: #10b981; }
.cat-shopping { background: #8b5cf6; }
.cat-rest { background: #94a3b8; }
.cat-default { background: #d1d5db; }

/* TIME EDITOR */
.time-editor { display: none; margin-top: 5px; }
.time-editor.open { display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; }
.time-editor input { border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; padding: 4px 8px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-family: inherit; width: 110px; }
.time-editor button { border: none; border-radius: 6px; padding: 4px 10px; font-size: 0.72rem; font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; }
.time-editor .btn-ok { background: var(--primary); color: white; }
.time-editor .btn-cancel { background: #f3f4f6; color: var(--muted); }

/* EDIT MODAL */
.modal-overlay { display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); z-index: 500; align-items: flex-end; }
.modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
.modal { background: white; border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0; padding: 20px 16px 30px; width: 100%; max-height: 85vh; overflow-y: auto; }
.modal h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.form-row { margin-bottom: 12px; }
.form-row label { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-weight: 600; }
.form-row input, .form-row textarea, .form-row select {
  width: 100%; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 8px 10px; font-size: 0.82rem; font-family: inherit; outline: none;
}
.form-row textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 70px; }
.form-actions { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 14px; }
.btn-primary { flex: 1; background: var(--primary); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 10px; padding: 11px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 700; }
.btn-secondary { flex: 1; background: #f3f4f6; color: var(--text); border: none; border-radius: 10px; padding: 11px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; }
.btn-danger-full { width: 100%; background: #fee2e2; color: #dc2626; border: none; border-radius: 10px; padding: 11px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 8px; font-weight: 700; }

/* FIREBASE SETUP MODAL */
.setup-overlay { display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); z-index: 600; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 20px; }
.setup-overlay.open { display: flex; }
.setup-box { background: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 22px 18px; width: 100%; max-width: 420px; }
.setup-box h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.setup-box p { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }

/* PARKING PANEL */
.parking-panel { display: none; background: #f8fafc; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 10px 12px; }
.parking-panel.open { display: block; }
.parking-lot-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 7px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; font-size: 0.73rem; }
.parking-lot-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.parking-search-btn { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 6px 14px; font-size: 0.75rem; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }

/* TOAST */
.toast { position: fixed; bottom: 20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(60px); background: #1e293b; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 24px; font-size: 0.8rem; transition: transform .3s; z-index: 999; white-space: nowrap; }
.toast.show { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }

/* ADD CARD (empty slot) */
.add-card { border: 1.5px dashed var(--border); border-radius: 12px; margin: 5px 0; padding: 10px 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; cursor: pointer; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.75rem; }
.add-card:hover { border-color: var(--primary-light); color: var(--primary); background: #f0fdf4; }

/* GAS STATION (day5) */
.gas-section { padding: 10px 12px; background: #fff7ed; border-top: 1px solid #fed7aa; }
.gas-title { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; color: #92400e; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.gas-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 5px 0; font-size: 0.73rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #fde8c8; }
.gas-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.gas-form { display: none; margin-top: 8px; }
.gas-form.open { display: block; }
.gas-form input { width: 100%; border: 1px solid #fed7aa; border-radius: 6px; padding: 6px 8px; font-size: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: inherit; }

/* WEATHER DETAIL */
.weather-detail { display: none; background: #e0f2fe; border-top: 1px solid #bae6fd; padding: 6px 14px; }
.weather-detail.open { display: flex; gap: 8px; overflow-x: auto; scrollbar-width: none; }
.weather-detail::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
.wh-item { flex-shrink: 0; text-align: center; font-size: 0.65rem; color: #0369a1; }
.wh-item .wh-time { font-weight: 700; }
.wh-item .wh-ic { font-size: 1rem; }

/* ── 드래그 중 텍스트 선택 방지 ── */
body.dragging-active,
body.dragging-active * { user-select: none !important; -webkit-user-select: none !important; cursor: grabbing !important; }

/* ── 스크롤 시 Firebase+날씨 접히는 영역 ── */
.collapsible-top {
  overflow: hidden;
  max-height: 200px;
  opacity: 1;
  transition: max-height 0.32s ease, opacity 0.22s ease;
}
.collapsible-top.collapsed {
  max-height: 0 !important;
  opacity: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* 날씨 바: 스크롤 시 접힘 (header/day-nav 사이에 위치) */
.weather-bar, .weather-detail {
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height 0.32s ease, opacity 0.22s ease, padding 0.22s ease;
  max-height: 200px;
  opacity: 1;
}
.sticky-top.scrolled .weather-bar {
  max-height: 0 !important;
  opacity: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  padding-top: 0 !important;
  padding-bottom: 0 !important;
}
.sticky-top.scrolled .weather-detail {
  max-height: 0 !important;
  opacity: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* 스크롤 후 header 슬림 */
.sticky-top.scrolled header {
  padding: 7px 16px 6px;
}
.sticky-top.scrolled header p,
.sticky-top.scrolled .header-meta { display: none; }
.sticky-top.scrolled header h1 { font-size: 1rem; }
header p, .header-meta {
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height 0.25s ease, opacity 0.2s ease, margin 0.2s ease;
  max-height: 60px; opacity: 1;
}
.sticky-top.scrolled header p,
.sticky-top.scrolled .header-meta {
  display: block !important;
  max-height: 0 !important;
  opacity: 0 !important;
  margin: 0 !important;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* ── 드롭 인서트 라인 ── */
.drop-indicator { height: 3px; background: #10b981; border-radius: 3px; margin: 2px 0; }
.sched-card.insert-above { border-top: 3px solid #10b981 !important; }
.sched-card.insert-below { border-bottom: 3px solid #10b981 !important; }

/* ── 일정추가 인라인 버튼 ── */
.meal-add-inline { background: none; border: 1.5px solid #d1fae5; border-radius: 20px; padding: 1px 8px; font-size: 0.62rem; color: #059669; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
.meal-add-inline:hover { background: #f0fdf4; }

/* ── 날씨 past ── */
.weather-day.past { opacity: 0.65; cursor: default; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="sticky-top" id="sticky-top">
  <div class="collapsible-top" id="collapsible-top">
    <div class="fb-banner" id="fb-banner">
      <span>🔥 Firebase</span>
      <span id="fb-status">⚠️ 미연결 — 로컬 저장만 사용 중</span>
      <button class="btn-fb" onclick="document.getElementById('setup-modal').classList.add('open')" style="margin-left:auto">🔗 공유 설정</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <header>
    <h1>✈️ 규슈 가족여행 플래너 🇯🇵</h1>
    <p>성인 2명 + 22개월 아기 · 렌터카 여행</p>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <span class="header-badge">📅 5월 23–27일</span>
      <span class="header-badge">📍 후쿠오카·기타큐슈·벳푸·유후인</span>
      <span class="header-badge">🍼 22개월 동반</span>
      <span class="header-badge"><span class="sync-dot" id="sync-dot"></span><span id="sync-label">오프라인</span></span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="weather-bar" id="weather-bar"><span class="weather-loading">🌤 날씨 불러오는 중...</span></div>
  <div class="weather-detail" id="weather-detail"></div>
  <nav class="day-nav" id="day-nav"></nav>
  <div class="nearby-strip">
    <span class="nearby-label">📍 현위치 근처:</span>
    <button class="nearby-btn" onclick="openNearby('cafe')">☕ 카페</button>
    <button class="nearby-btn" onclick="openNearby('uniqlo')">👕 유니클로</button>
    <button class="nearby-btn" onclick="openNearby('convenience')">🏪 편의점</button>
    <button class="nearby-btn" onclick="openNearby('baby')">🍼 유아용품점</button>
  </div>
</div>

<main id="main-content"></main>

<div class="modal-overlay" id="edit-modal">
  <div class="modal">
    <h3 id="edit-modal-title">일정 수정</h3>
    <div class="form-row"><label>장소명</label><input id="edit-title" type="text"/></div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>카테고리</label>
      <select id="edit-cat">
        <option value="transport">🚗 이동/교통</option>
        <option value="restaurant">🍴 식사</option>
        <option value="attraction">🏯 관광/체험</option>
        <option value="shopping">🛍 쇼핑</option>
        <option value="rest">🏨 숙소/휴식</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>날짜</label>
      <select id="edit-day"></select>
    </div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>섹션</label>
      <select id="edit-meal">
        <option value="breakfast">🌅 조식</option>
        <option value="morning">🌤 오전</option>
        <option value="lunch">🍱 중식</option>
        <option value="afternoon">🌇 오후</option>
        <option value="dinner">🌙 석식</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>시간 (선택)</label><input id="edit-time" type="text" placeholder="예: 12:30"/></div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>메모</label><textarea id="edit-desc"></textarea></div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>구글맵 검색어</label><input id="edit-map" type="text"/></div>
    <div class="form-actions">
      <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="closeEditModal()">취소</button>
      <button class="btn-primary" onclick="saveEdit()">저장</button>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-danger-full" onclick="deleteCard()">🗑 이 일정 삭제</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal-overlay" id="add-modal">
  <div class="modal">
    <h3>일정 추가</h3>
    <div class="form-row"><label>장소명</label><input id="add-title" type="text" placeholder="예: 유후인 플로럴 빌리지"/></div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>카테고리</label>
      <select id="add-cat">
        <option value="attraction">🏯 관광/체험</option>
        <option value="restaurant">🍴 식사</option>
        <option value="transport">🚗 이동/교통</option>
        <option value="shopping">🛍 쇼핑</option>
        <option value="rest">🏨 숙소/휴식</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>메모</label><textarea id="add-desc" placeholder="메모 (선택)"></textarea></div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>시간 (선택)</label><input id="add-time" type="text" placeholder="예: 14:00"/></div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>구글맵 검색어</label><input id="add-map" type="text" placeholder="예: 유후인역 주차장"/></div>
    <div class="form-actions">
      <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="closeAddModal()">취소</button>
      <button class="btn-primary" onclick="saveAdd()">추가</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="setup-overlay" id="setup-modal">
  <div class="setup-box">
    <h3>🔥 Firebase 동기화 설정</h3>
    <p>Firebase를 연결하면 두 기기에서 실시간 공유가 됩니다. 사용하지 않아도 로컬 저장은 정상 동작합니다.</p>
    <div class="form-row"><label>API Key</label><input id="fb-apikey" type="text" placeholder="AIza..."/></div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>Auth Domain</label><input id="fb-authdomain" type="text" placeholder="xxx.firebaseapp.com"/></div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>Project ID</label><input id="fb-projectid" type="text" placeholder="your-project-id"/></div>
    <div class="form-row"><label>App ID</label><input id="fb-appid" type="text" placeholder="1:xxx:web:xxx"/></div>
    <div class="form-actions">
      <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="document.getElementById('setup-modal').classList.remove('open')">나중에</button>
